---
// No props – static CTA
---

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: #0a0a0f;
    padding: 8rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  /* Violet gradient glow from top */
  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(127,119,221,0.35), transparent);
  }
  .cta-section::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 400px; height: 220px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(127,119,221,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #F0EFFF;
    line-height: 1.1;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }
  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: rgba(240,239,255,0.45);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: #7F77DD;
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 200ms;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: #6B63C9; }
  .cta-email {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(240,239,255,0.25);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 150ms;
  }
  .cta-email:hover { color: rgba(240,239,255,0.55); }
</style>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div style="position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:72rem; margin:0 auto; padding:0 2rem;">
    <h2 class="cta-headline">
      Bereit für deinen<br/>
      <span style="color:#7F77DD;">digitalen Auftritt?</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="cta-sub">
      Kostenloses Erstgespräch – ich analysiere deine Situation und zeige dir konkret, was möglich ist.
    </p>
    <a href="/kontakt" class="cta-btn">Jetzt Gespräch buchen</a>
    <a href="mailto:mbourkiah@k-solutions.biz" class="cta-email">
      oder schreib direkt: mbourkiah@k-solutions.biz
    </a>
    <p style="margin-top:3rem; font-size:12px; color:rgba(240,239,255,0.18);">
      📍 Aus Köln &nbsp;·&nbsp; 48h Antwortzeit &nbsp;·&nbsp; Keine versteckten Kosten
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
